革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/hWh5Sax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWh5Sax.jpg&h=f682f165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15c9f91bd60793e439e3cd7ed28659b38df70464","tid":1389067,"uid":251691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89cf6a9f8ec4f915a46ef5e947d1b879b2596c64","tid":1389067,"uid":41784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"我打機見木長盾加幾層物流用嘅捆膜，防禦力上升好多又唔會加負重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"包多幾層 其實可能已經擋到海綿彈"},{"pid":"042196fe496823910c1205e77d78c914da424eee","tid":1389067,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4aa4bde60211fdf574d3d622b8695a213c8f667","tid":1389067,"uid":39752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"re